<plot>Power generation is industrial, hidden away, misunderstood. Electroland takes an aesthetic approach to it, going deep into the inner workings of the world's electric grid to show the imposing beauty of different power generation methods from coal to solar. Electroland shows the ingenuity of power production, educating an audience of power users to understand the origins of the electricity they use.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?175017</url></doc>
